{"tid":1627603,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大膽建議","createTime":"2019-10-05T16:42:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T18:38:48.000Z","uid":320624,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3660bf78ca4fad3743f76665a00a7a4b65ec8130","tid":1627603,"uid":320624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:42:38.000Z","msg":"有冇人覺得前線可以「軍隊化」，有<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>統一指揮</strong></span></span><br />\n同埋<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一層一層嘅架構</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n即係有人發號施令和通知各大隊，大隊協調各小隊，小隊隊長分工俾唔同隊員。<br />\n好似d軍隊咁<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">唔知可唔可行？</span><br />\n利申：我冇上過前線<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n前線手足，無論你們怎樣，我都會愛你們啊 (つ≧▽≦)つ<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n祝各位武運昌隆"},{"pid":"78a9de5171a4f5c002661548b87fa51ab03e611d","tid":1627603,"uid":320624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:50:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bfc8d9ec766ce726bdefecc1484e1de54fad138","tid":1627603,"uid":320624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:51:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99b65d4d3063a7a2936bdaaaf1064fc517ffafd0","tid":1627603,"uid":320624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:51:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c3db8acc547b96cbce13471d8a9fcde61a2ab44","tid":1627603,"uid":320624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco